reviewText: good movie i just wish it had more race footage

definately more than just motorcycles,about settng a goal and persevering and acheiving that goal no matter the obstacles that you have to overcome,great strength and determination,brute willpower,I absolutely loved it,two thumbs up!
Great Doc. Wanted more riding scenes.
Inspirational and a great look behind the scenes of the Dakar rally.

Awesome movie! Must buy for any Dakar fan!
Fast delivery. Great great!
Great story of the little guy taking on a giant of an adventure.
Fast shipping, well packed and as described - will shop again
Wasn't bad but I've seen better, a lot better.
Compelling store line, great scenes, wish there was a little footage of the actually rider.

These guys put out a tremendous effort to complete the Dakar and to make a movie. The least I can do is buy a disc. The movie is totally worth it to see how a one-man privateer can persevere and complete the race. Outstanding effort.
Right up there with dust to glory. I really enjoyed it and would buy it again!

A cool movie about a racer living out his dream at an epic world famous event.
It's no "On Any Sunday", but you should own it if you're a motorcycle guy.
